title: Indian Bridge Collapse Casts Harsh Spotlight on Safety Practices
description: Police say a business without expertise in bridge repairs was tasked with renovating a small town’s star attraction.

title: U.K. Sees Record Numbers of Migrants Crossing English Channel in Small Boats
description: The British asylum system is overwhelmed by migrants from both developing countries and more stable nations such as Albania, officials say.

title: Behind Benjamin Netanyahu's Win in Israel: The Rise of Religious Zionism
description: An ultranationalist political outlook forged in Jewish West Bank settlements could play a central role in Israel’s next government.

title: Ukraine Accuses Iran of Training Russian Drone Pilots
description: Drone strikes on civilian targets across Ukraine have been so damaging that the capital’s mayor urged residents to consider temporarily leaving the city.

title: West Sees Little Choice but to Keep Backing Ukraine
description: Washington and its allies see little prospect of a negotiated end to the war in Ukraine soon given the high stakes for Moscow and Kyiv, and the fact that both sides believe they can win, Western diplomats say.

title: COP27 Summit Begins as Economy, Ukraine War Overshadow Climate Concerns
description: Geopolitical and economic upheaval has stalled progress and led to backsliding by some measures over the past year, but countries are spending more to address climate change.
